subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Brice Johnson had career highs of 39 points and 23 rebounds, leading No. 6 North Carolina (14-2, 3-0 Atlantic Coast Conference) to a 106-90 victory at Florida State (10-4, 0-2) on Monday night.
